OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FShowers
OL,6,Fand winds ease from west Friday.
OL,7,FBright start Saturday cloud and rain
OL,8,Fedging east in afternoon. Morning rain
OL,9,FSunday then sunny spells and a few
OL,10,Fshowers in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
